Subject: [PATCH 20/22] =?UTF-8?q?fix:=20v0.1=20T2a=20=E2=80=94=20restrict?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20to=20closed=20goals=20(empty=20user=20context),=20capture-fr?=
 =?UTF-8?q?ee=20by=20construction?=
